    <entry>
      <title>PostgreBDR</title>
      <link href="/postPostgreBDR/"/>
      <url>/postPostgreBDR/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Halo,</p><p>Kali ini saya akan menjelaskan tentang PostgresBDR.</p><h5 id="1-Apa-Itu-PostgresBDR"><a href="#1-Apa-Itu-PostgresBDR" class="headerlink" title="1. Apa Itu PostgresBDR ?"></a>1. Apa Itu PostgresBDR ?</h5><p>PostgresBDR adalah sebuah aplikasi dari PostgreSQL, yang mana berfungsi sebagai replikasi database server. Spesifik nya replikasi database server master to master</p><p>Apa itu replikasi database ?, replikasi database adalah suatu sistem dimana fungsi nya sebagai backup dari database utama, ketika database utama mengalami error maka query yang masuk akan diproses oleh database  replikasi. </p><p>Berikut cara instalasi PostgresBDR di sistem operasi Ubuntu 18.04 :</p><ul><li>Menginstall Postgres-BDR melalui apt </li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo sh -c &apos;echo &quot;deb http://apt.postgresql.org/pub/repos/apt/ $(lsb_release -cs)-pgdg main&quot; &gt; /etc/apt/sources.list.d/pgdg.list&apos;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo sh -c &apos;echo &quot;deb [arch=amd64] http://packages.2ndquadrant.com/bdr/apt/ $(lsb_release -cs)-2ndquadrant main&quot; &gt; /etc/apt/sources.list.d/2ndquadrant.list&apos;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install wget ca-certificates</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wget --quiet -O - https://www.postgresql.org/media/keys/ACCC4CF8.asc | sudo apt-key add -</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wget --quiet -O - http://packages.2ndquadrant.com/bdr/apt/AA7A6805.asc | sudo apt-key add -</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get upgrade</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install postgresql-bdr-9.4 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">postgresql-bdr-9.4-bdr-plugin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Kalau tidak bisa melalui tutorial diatas, silakan untuk mencoba menginstall postgres-bdr nya melalui link berikut : <a href="https://www.2ndquadrant.com/en/resources/bdr/bdr-installation-instructions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.2ndquadrant.com/en/resources/bdr/bdr-installation-instructions/</a></p><ul><li>Buat directory postgresBDR, dan setting path serta inisiasi db </li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su -l postgres</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=/usr/lib/postgresql/9.4/bin:$PATH</span><br><span class="line">mkdir $HOME/9.4-bdr</span><br><span class="line">initdb -D $HOME/9.4-bdr -A trust</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Edit file konfigurasi $HOME/9.4-bdr/postgresql.conf, menjadi berikut :</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">listen_addresses = &apos;*&apos;</span><br><span class="line">shared_preload_libraries = &apos;bdr&apos;</span><br><span class="line">wal_level = &apos;logical&apos;</span><br><span class="line">track_commit_timestamp = on</span><br><span class="line">max_connections = 100</span><br><span class="line">max_wal_senders = 10</span><br><span class="line">max_replication_slots = 10</span><br><span class="line">max_worker_processes = 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Lalu selanjutnya edit file konfigurasi $HOME/9.4-bdr/pg_hba.conf, menjadi berikut :</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local   replication     postgres                                trust</span><br><span class="line">host    replication     postgres        127.0.0.1/32            trust</span><br><span class="line">host    replication     postgres        ::1/128                 trust</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">host all all 0.0.0.0/0  password</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">host replication postgres IP Server1/32 trust</span><br><span class="line">host replication postgres IP Server2/32 trust</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">host replication bdrsync IP Server1/32 password</span><br><span class="line">host replication bdrsync IP Server2/32 password</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Setelah itu, silakan untuk menonaktifkan service PostgreSQL Anda lalu aktifkan service Postgres-BDR Anda. Setelah Postgres-BDR Anda aktif, silakan membuat user untuk Master dan set privileges nya menjadi superuser.</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pg_ctl -D $HOME/9.4/main stop</span><br><span class="line">pg_ctl -D $HOME/9.4-bdr start</span><br><span class="line">psql -c &quot;CREATE USER bdrsync superuser;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">psql -c &quot;ALTER USER bdrsync WITH PASSWORD &apos;12345#&apos;;&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Create user biasa dan create database, serta set owner database Anda. Lalu tambahkan ekstensi bdr pada database Anda.</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">createuser masterbdr</span><br><span class="line">createdb -O masterbdr testbdr</span><br><span class="line">psql testbdr -c &apos;CREATE EXTENSION btree_gist;&apos;</span><br><span class="line">psql testbdr -c &apos;CREATE EXTENSION bdr;&apos;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Setelah konfigurasi database master 1 dan database master 2, silakan membuat grup replikasi pada master 1, berikut :</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">psql</span><br><span class="line">\c testbdr</span><br><span class="line">SELECT bdr.bdr_group_create(</span><br><span class="line">    local_node_name := &apos;node1&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">    node_external_dsn := &apos;host=IPServer1 user=bdrsync dbname=testbdr password=password user bdrsync&apos;</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Apabila Anda sudah membuat grup replikasi database pada master 1. Anda dapat membuat master 2 join ke grup master 1. </li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">psql</span><br><span class="line">\c testbdr</span><br><span class="line">SELECT bdr.bdr_group_join(</span><br><span class="line">    local_node_name := &apos;node2&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">    node_external_dsn := &apos;host=IPServer2 user=bdrsync dbname=testbdr password=12345#&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">    join_using_dsn := &apos;host=IPServer1 user=bdrsync dbname=testbdr password=12345#&apos;</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Note-Anda-tidak-perlu-membuat-grup-pada-master-2-Anda-hanya-perlu-membuat-master-2-join-ke-grup-master-1"><a href="#Note-Anda-tidak-perlu-membuat-grup-pada-master-2-Anda-hanya-perlu-membuat-master-2-join-ke-grup-master-1" class="headerlink" title="Note: Anda tidak perlu membuat grup pada master 2, Anda hanya perlu membuat master 2 join ke grup master 1."></a>Note: Anda tidak perlu membuat grup pada master 2, Anda hanya perlu membuat master 2 join ke grup master 1.</h5><p>Itulah sedikit informasi yang bisa saya sampaikan mengenai Postgres-BDR, see you on the next post, thanks ! :)</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Struktur Server Blocks Nginx</title>
      <link href="/postStruktur-Server-Blocks-Nginx-1/"/>
      <url>/postStruktur-Server-Blocks-Nginx-1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://backup1.s3-id-jkt-1.kilatstorage.id/nginx-logo.jpg" alt="nginx" title="An nginx"></p><p>Halo,</p><p>Saat ini saya akan mencoba menjelaskan sedikit tentang struktur ServerBlocks atau biasa dikenal dengan VirtualHost untuk Web Server Nginx. </p><p>Sebelumnya sudah tau fungsi dari VirtualHost atau ServerBlocks itu apa ? VirtualHost atau ServerBlocks adalah suatu file yang berisi seluruh konfigurasi dari website Anda, yang nantinya dibaca dan dieksekusi oleh Web Server.</p><h3 id="Berikut-contoh-Struktur-ServerBlocks-pada-Nginx"><a href="#Berikut-contoh-Struktur-ServerBlocks-pada-Nginx" class="headerlink" title="Berikut contoh Struktur ServerBlocks pada Nginx :"></a>Berikut contoh Struktur ServerBlocks pada Nginx :</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">server &#123; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">listen 80; #listen port web server</span><br><span class="line">server_name amar2414.id; #nama domain/website Anda</span><br><span class="line">root /path/directory_root/website_Anda;</span><br><span class="line">error_log /path/directory/errorlog/website_Anda;</span><br><span class="line">index index.php index.html #directory index website Anda, dimana web server akan secara default mengekseskusi file index paling kiri (prioritas).</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">location / &#123; Konfigurasi untuk URI</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">location ~ \.php$ &#123;  #Konfigurasi untuk php-fpm</span><br><span class="line">                try_files $uri /index.php = 404;</span><br><span class="line">                include fastcgi_params;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_intercept_errors on;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php-fpm/php-fpm.sock;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_index index.php;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Sekian struktur ServerBlocks yang dapat saya jelaskan, terima kasih!  :)</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
